      "description": "Up for sale is a vehicle in fair condition that serves as a reliable daily driver but does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear bumper, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to put in a little elbow grease or looking for an affordable entry-level option.",
