    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in absolute showroom condition. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards, preserving its original luster and mechanical integrity. With an interior that remains indistinguishable from new and a performance profile that mirrors its factory debut, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
