    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total dream. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garage-kept and kept sparkling. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition, looking and smelling just like it did on the showroom floor. Whether you're cruising on the weekend or just want something that turns heads, this beauty is ready for a new home. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look and let's chat!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
