      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a surgically maintained E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s specimen. The S54 straight-six has been meticulously sorted with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. Power delivery is linear and visceral, channeled through a crisp Getrag 6-speed with zero synchro drag. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a bespoke suspension geometry tuned for neutral turn-in and high-speed stability. No parasitic fluid loss, no deferred maintenance\u2014just a pure, analog masterpiece that performs with more precision today than it did off the assembly line. This is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
